title.rendered: CityWalk Wins Excellence in Construction Award

content.rendered: Alticor Inc is proud to announce that in early August, the Southeast District received a prestigious Eagle Award from the Associated Builders and Contractors Central Florida Chapter for their Excellence in Construction Awards Program. This award is for the CityWalk Venue Renovations Project in the Commercial – Renovation, $20-$50 million category. The awards banquet will be held on Saturday, October 24, at the Hyatt Regency Orlando. Congratulations to the entire project team on this prestigious win!
